:''This article deals with an aspect of celebrity, for the Record Label, see [[Household Name Records]]''

A '''household name''' ([[noun]]) is a brand that is well known to the great majority of households. This brand may represent any type of product or person - a celebrity may be referred to as being a household name. Examples of the previously mentioned may include: [[Big Mac]], [[David Beckham]].

A household name may also be a noun form of an [[Genericized trademark|aneponym]], where the name comes to replace its own definition. A notable exception would be [[Coke]] and [[Pepsi]], neither of which represents an aneponym, but both of whom are well established household names.